PulseAudio Control

The [prgm]pa[/prgm] command manages the active PulseAudio sink.

Set the default sink

$ [prgm]pa list-sinks[/prgm]                    # Show available audio outputs
$ [prgm]pa set-default-sink[/prgm] [arg-value]hdmi[/arg-value]         # Switch to HDMI output

Check what sink different outputs are playing on

$ [prgm]pa list-sink-inputs[/prgm]            # Show active audio streams

The sink pattern matches against device names or descriptions.
